messages.message: Hey, seems like my PR's cypress tests are failing because it can't successfully get the sandbox running for them. Anyone else running into this?

as Udit mentioned, all frontend PRs are blocked on Cypress CI since Crafting sandbox deployments are currently broken

we hope to fix this by EOD (either by rotating the ssh key for the Crafting service account or by creating a new service account)

if you have any PRs that need to urgently be merged, please run Cypress tests against your branch manually and ping a manager for a force-merge
This should be fixed now if people need to rerun CI on their PRs!
